**HTML Email Layout for Promotional Campaign**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Healthcare Kit Offer</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        /* Email Container */
       .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Header Section */
       .header-section {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
        }

        /* Content Section */
       .content-section {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Call-to-Action Section */
       .call-to-action-section {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Button Styles */
       .btn {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Link Styles */
       .link {
            color: #337ab7;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header-section">
            <h2>Get Your Free Healthcare Kit!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content-section">
            <p>Dear valued customer,</p>
            <p>Thank you for your feedback on our recent healthcare kit offer. We value your opinion and would like to continue improving our products to meet your needs.</p>
            <p>To help us better understand your preferences, we invite you to participate in our quick 5-minute survey. Your input will be invaluable in shaping our future product offerings.</p>
            <p><a class="link" href="https://example.com/survey">Take the survey now!</a></p>
            <p>As a token of appreciation, we would like to offer you a FREE healthcare kit, complete with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>First-aid kit</li>
                <li>Health monitoring devices</li>
                <li>Wellness guides</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Please click the button below to redeem your free kit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="call-to-action-section">
            <button class="btn">Redeem Your Free Kit Now!</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```
**How it works:**

1. The email layout consists of a container with a header section, content section, and call-to-action section.
2. The header section displays the promotional offer and includes a call-to-action button to take the survey.
3. The content section provides more information about the survey, the healthcare kit, and
